  • All Classes Class Summary Exception Summary 
    Class Description
    AxisHelper
    This is an Object3d that contains data for the x, y and z axis.
    BoundingBox
    Axis aligned bounding box from a source point cloud.
    BoxEdgesGeometry
    Geometry containing the necessary buffer data to draw the edges of a box.
    BufferLayout
    Keeps structural and size-related information concerning the layout of a VertexBufferObject, such as position, color, texture coordinates etc.
    Camera
    Base camera class.
    CloudGeometryBuilder
    Base class for cloud data extractor (base rgb, normal rgb, qhull ).
    CloudGeometryConstructor
    Director class for the CloudGeometryBuilder.
    CloudLoader
    Generates a float buffer from a point cloud text file.
    Configuration
    The state of the application at a given time; acts like a controller (a bridge of communication between the view and the model) for the application within the MCV model.
    Controls
    Base class for camera controls; listens for mouse input.
    DirectoryLoader
    Used for validating and loading a Semviz directory.
    ElementBufferObject
    Also called index buffer object, it allows re-using points in a VertexBufferObject multiple times to draw shapes composed of two or more triangles having common points.
    Geometry
    Basic geometry grouping vertex data and buffer layout.
    GraphicsUtils
    Offers some tools allowing to manipulated some graphical data.
    HighResolutionCloudBuilder
    Concrete cloud builder that extracts the x, y, z, r, g, b GL vertex buffer data from a point cloud; this generates the high resolution geometry of the base cloud.
    InvalidDirectoryException  
    MainWindow  
    NormalColoredCloudBuilder
    Concrete cloud builder that extracts the x, y, z, normalX, normalY, normalZ GL vertex buffer data from a point cloud; this generates the high resolution geometry of the base cloud, but instead of displaying each vertex in its original color, its color is generated from the components of the normal vector in it.
    Object3d
    Generic representation of a 3d object.
    OrbitControls
    Controls making the camera move around its target.
    OrthographicCamera
    Cube view camera.
    PerspectiveCamera
    Camera offering a perspective (real-life) view of the scene.
    Point
    Structure containing the color and the normals in addition to a point's coordinates.
    PointCloud
    Collection of points.
    QHullBuilder
    This cloud builder generates the convex hull geometry of a point cloud; the color of the hull is given by the normal vector to the plane given by the cloud.
    QueryManager  
    QueryResult  
    Renderer
    Renders a scene with a camera on a canvas.
    Scene
    Collection of 3d geometries to be rendered.
    SemvizException  
    ShaderProgram
    Shader program that runs on the GPU.
    SuperCloud
    When executing a SPARQL query via QueryManager, multiple cloud individuals are retrieved.
    TransformationUtils
    Provides a series of mathematical tools for affine transformations.
    VertexArrayObject
    Stores the layout for one or more VertexBufferObject instances.
    VertexBufferObject
    Stores the raw data concerning what is to be drawn by OpenGL, such as vertex positions, colors, texture coordinates etc.
    VertexDataReader
    Basic text file reader, retrieving vertex buffer data separated by spaces and lines.
    Viewer
    Structure gathering a scene, camera, renderer configuration that allows navigating a scene of three-dimensional object around an orbit.
    ViewItem
    Stores geometric information about a given cloud, so that it is not recalculated each time the display mode of the cloud is changed.
